      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why i'm still typing this. everything just feels like such a massive weight lately. the lab results came back again and it's just... nothing. months of work gone. my funding is basically non-existent now and i feel like i'm just sinking. i'm so incredibly tired of fighting for something that clearly doesn't want me. i just want everything to stop.",
